        "650": {
          "vnum": 650,
          "name": "Grassy Hills",
          "description": "The game trail that led you into the hills, far from town, is completely gone now. It's not like you could really get lost out here with all the high ground to get your bearings, but it definitely feels like you're out in the middle of nowhere. The spoor of some carnivorous animal litters the area.",
