        "651": {
          "vnum": 651,
          "name": "Rocky Dell",
          "description": "Here in this shallow patch of land, the pastel green hills begin to give way to the stony foothills east of Mount M'chel. Most of the area is still verdant and grassy, but a large patch in front of a cave in a stone bluff has been tramped flat by passage of many paws.",
