        "652": {
          "vnum": 652,
          "name": "Cramped Tunnel",
          "description": "The opening of the cave was deceptively large, and you find the tunnel quickly closing in on you. Eventually it becomes necessary to lay flat and wriggle your way along. Better hope you don't meet up with the cave's occupant, unless you think you can fight it off with your face.",
