        "653": {
          "vnum": 653,
          "name": "Coyote's Den",
          "description": "The cramped tunnel opens up into a cozy little chamber in the natural rock. Dried grass lines most of the floor, and a natural chimney leading to a tiny opening above you lets in a little fresh air. Several mewling pups roll about in a fluffy pile.",
