        "654": {
          "vnum": 654,
          "name": "Stony Foothills",
          "description": "You are surprised to be following a path all the way out here in the boonies. The ground is rocky with sparse vegetation, and the trail is not the result of any passing game. The way is picked out with determined thought, and marked periodically with piles of stones.",
