          "vnum": 656,
          "name": "Narrow Vale",
          "description": "The twisting path straightens out as it leads into a small vale. The path ahead is obscured by a rise in the terrain, but farther along a thin pillar of natural looking stone rises up into the sky. Many of the trees in this area have been felled and dragged away, likely to build shelters.",
