        "1683": {
          "vnum": 1683,
          "name": "The Green Hilly Plain",
          "description": "Hills of grassy green flow in all directions like huge earthen ocean swells. Thinking about them in these terms makes you suddenly feel very much like you've been left in the middle of the sea on a tiny raft, except there's no such thing as a land shark. Well, not around Mareldja there isn't.",
