        "614": {
          "vnum": 614,
          "name": "Path Away from J'rel",
          "description": "Green. An even carpet of it, made of low grassy growth, is the canvas upon which little detail is painted. A gradual rise succeeds in concealing the town of J'rel, and away from it Luukir dot the landscape sparsely. The trail continues to the north, the only path worth following, and a dusty point of gathering is ahead.",
