        "636": {
          "vnum": 636,
          "name": "A Muddy Trail",
          "description": "There can be no question now that this trail is leading to the mountain you saw all the way back from J'rel. This is a trade road and there must be something in that mountain that men and elves come to steal for money. There isn't a hint of entering the rocky foothills however.",
