        "638": {
          "vnum": 638,
          "name": "A Small Graveyard",
          "description": "Bent ironwork, fine and low, somberly defines this area from the surrounding plain as a graveyard. Several score headstones fill it save a very few empty patches. This place must be reserved for miners, as you gather that J'relians typically cremate, but how many must work here for there to be so many dead?",
          "grid_x": -2,
          "grid_y": -3,
          "exits": {
            "w": {
