        "645": {
          "vnum": 645,
          "name": "A Green Hilltop",
          "description": "You ascend the hillside and are rewarded with a diverse panorama. Far to the southeast the bustling town of J'rel stands. On its outskirts and moving out to your east and north as far as you can see lie rolling green hills, which you traversed in part to get here. To the northwest a great mountain rises into the clouds -- surely the hub of many lands. And just to your west and south a murky fog spreads forth until it distantly meets the river Frektal.",
          "grid_x": 0,
          "grid_y": 15,
          "exits": {
